Subject: [PATCH] ui: split view — tile 2–4 WebContents in one window

Adds a SplitViewLayout manager to BrowserView that tiles 2–4 active
WebContents in a single window. Each tile is a full WebContents with
its own navigation bar.

Layouts:
  - Vertical split (left | right)
  - Horizontal split (top | bottom)
  - 2×2 grid

Triggered by:
  - Dragging a tab from the sidebar onto another tab (drop zone appears)
  - Keyboard shortcut: Cmd/Ctrl+Shift+\ (toggle split)
  - Context menu on a tab: "Open in split view"

Dividers are draggable; position persisted per workspace.

TODO: Stub. Full implementation in Phase 2.
